McDonald ' s launches 30 bln yen / $ Samurai . McDonald ' s Corp launched 30 billion yen worth of 5 . 0 percent dual - currency samurai bonds due May 16 , 2000 , market sources said on Thursday . The issue was priced at par and the coupon will be paid on May 16 annually . The subscription period runs from October 31 to November 18 and the payment is due on November 19 , they said . McDonald ' s has ratings of Aa2 from Moody ' s Investor Service and AA from Standard and Poors . - - - Tokyo Treasury Desk 813 - 3432 - 8676 
